quran[27]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,94,"àti wíwọ inú iná Jẹhīm."
  56,95,"Dájúdájú èyí, òhun ni òdodo tó dájú."
  56,96,"Nítorí náà, ṣàfọ̀mọ́ fún orúkọ Olúwa rẹ, Atóbi."
  68,28,"Ẹni tó dúró déédé jùlọ nínú wọn sọ pé: “Ṣé èmi kò sọ fún yín pé ẹ̀yin kò ṣe ṣàfọ̀mọ́ fún Allāhu (pé “a máa kórè oko wa, ’in ṣā ’Allāhu.)”?"
  68,29,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Mímọ́ ni fún Olúwa wa, dájúdájú àwa jẹ́ alábòsí.”"
  68,30,"Apá kan wọn kọjú sí apá kan; wọ́n sì ń dára wọn lẹ́bi."
  69,25,"Ní ti ẹni tí wọ́n bá sì fún ní tírà rẹ̀ ní ọwọ́ òsì rẹ̀, ó máa wí pé: “Háà! Kí wọ́n sì má fún mi ni tírà mi!{1}.",1:[Aláìgbàgbọ́ máa tì ọwọ́ òsì rẹ̀ bọ inú igbá-àyà rẹ̀ bọ́ sí ẹ̀yìn rẹ̀ láti fi gba ìwé iṣẹ́ rẹ̀.]
  69,26,"Àti pé kí èmi sì má mọ ohun tí ìṣírò-iṣẹ́ mi jẹ́."
  69,27,"Háà! Kí ikú sì jẹ́ òpin (ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀dá)."
  70,19,"Dájúdájú ènìyàn, A ṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀ ní aláìlọ́kàn, ọ̀kánjúà."
  70,20,"Nígbà tí aburú bá fọwọ́ bà á, ó máa kanra gógó."
  70,21,"Nígbà tí ọwọ́ rẹ̀ bá sì ba oore, ó máa yahun."
  71,16,"Ó sì ṣe òṣùpá ní ìmọ́lẹ̀ sínú wọn. Ó tún ṣe òòrùn ní àtùpà."
  71,17,"Allāhu mu yín jáde láti ara erùpẹ̀ ilẹ̀."
  71,18,"Lẹ́yìn náà, Ó máa da yín padà sínú rẹ̀. Ó sì máa mu yín jáde tààrà."
  72,13,"Dájúdájú nígbà tí a gbọ́ nípa ìmọ̀nà (láti inú al-Ƙur’ān), a gbà á gbọ́. Nítorí náà, ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo nínú Olúwa rẹ̀, kí ó má bẹ̀rù àdínkù(nínú ẹ̀san rere) àti (àlékún) aburú.{1}.",1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, wọn kò níí dín ẹ̀san iṣẹ́ rere onígbàgbọ́ òdodo kù, wọn kò sì níí fi kún àṣìṣe rẹ̀. Àti pé, àforíjìn Allāhu súnmọ́ ọn pẹ́kípẹ́kí lórí àwọn àṣìṣe náà.]
  72,14,"Dájúdájú àwọn mùsùlùmí wà nínú wa. Àwọn arúfin náà wà nínú wa. Nítorí náà, ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá ṣe ’Islām, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni wọ́n ṣe àwárí ìmọ̀nà.”"
  72,15,"Ní ti àwọn arúfin, àwọn ni wọ́n máa jẹ́ igi ìkoná fún iná Jahanamọ.”"
  73,7,"Dájúdájú iṣẹ́ púpọ̀ wà fún ọ ní ọ̀sán."
  73,8,"Rántí orúkọ Olúwa rẹ. Kí o sì da ọkàn kọ Ọ́ pátápátá."
  73,9,"Olúwa ibùyọ òòrùn àti ibùwọ̀ òòrùn, kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí ẹ gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àfi Òun. Nítorí náà, mú Un ní Aláfẹ̀yìntì."
  74,4,"Aṣọ rẹ ni kí o fọ̀ mọ́."
  74,5,"Òrìṣà ni kí o jìnnà sí."
  74,6,"Má ṣe tọrẹ nítorí kí o lè rí púpọ̀ gbà."
  75,1,"Èmi (Allāhu) ń fi Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde búra."
  75,2,"Mo tún ń fi ẹ̀mí tó máa dá ara rẹ̀ ní ẹ̀bi búra."
  75,3,"Ṣé ènìyàn lérò pé A kò níí kó àwọn eegun rẹ̀ jọ ni?"